///
/// Introduction
@NODE INTR "Introduction"

    @{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}


Combo2/@{"Tester2" LINK TES2} programme set is dedicated to run and
service Combo2/Combo3 programmer.

Hardware features:

 · Connects by RS-232 (56 or 19.2 kbps)
 · Controlled by internal AT89C51 processor
 · Works under DOS, MS Windows 95, 98, 98SE, Me, NT40, 2000, XP, AmigaOS 3.0+, MorphOS 1.4+
 · Powered by external power supply adaptor (battery) 12V
 · Doesn't require any adapters - every chipset has got its own socket
 · Green LED indicates power supply,
   red LED indicates work in progress
 · Small dimensions (comfortable to use with laptop)
 · Integrated ISP socket makes possible programming "in system" of
   EEPROM, PIC and AVR chipsets
 · Fast work (optimal write/clear times)


Combo2 software features:

 · Stable and reliable work
 · Very easy and clear usage
 · All strings are localized (a few language version available)
 · Documentation in form of guide file
 · Reads HEX, BIN, IHX, EEP files
 · Programme allows edition of data and reading HEX files with incorrect CRC

@{i}You can find more information about COMBO2/COMBO3 project in the internet:
    <http://www.progstar.com.pl/combo3/>

And under:
    <http://www.comboamiga.republika.pl>
you can find the latest version of Combo2 software for Amiga and Pegasos computers.
@{ui}
@ENDNODE
///
/// Requirements
@NODE REQU "Requirements"

    @{b}@{u}Requirements@{uu}@{ub}


Available software should work properly with AmigaOS v3.0+

Programme also requires following elements:
 · gadtools.library (39+)
 · asl.libraty (38+)
 · system screen in at least 640x480 resolution

Programme had been written and tested on Amiga 1200 with MC040/25MHz
processor and AmigaOS 3.9.

From version 3.0+ the programme is written and tested on Pegasos with MorphOS.
Also compatibility with OS3.1 (WinUAE emulator), OS3.9 and OS4.0 is tested.

                     @{b}This software is freeware.@{ub}
@{b}Note:@{ub}
@{u}The consent of the author is needed to place the programme archive on
any kind of publication of commercial character.@{uu}
@{fg shine}It is not allowed to publish any part of the archive separately!@{fg text}

Please inform about all problems with software or bugs:

